snippet.title: NodeRunner Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Store Page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2850830/NodeRunner/

Itch.io Store Page:
https://aaronbacon.itch.io/noderunner-deluxe

NodeRunner is a Fast-paced Physics Roguelike where you fling yourself from Node to Node to run from the ever-approaching Chaser. Collect Mods, Collect Weapons, then turn your guns to the Chaser to take it down. 

NodeRunner Credits:
Designed and Programmed by Aaron Brownlee
Shop Mod Icons designed by Shona Callanan
Music and Sound Effects by David Cowley
